HEADWORD: Supercrescence
<hw>Su`per*cres"cence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Supercrescent</er>.]</ety> <def>That which grows upon another
growing thing; a parasite.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir T.
